{
  "texts": [
    "Descriptive statistics was used to provide an overview of the dataset.",
    "Depending on the nature of the variables the results are reported either as percentages or as medians with interquartile range (IQR).",
    "Comparison among percentages were performed with the chi-square test with a p-values significance threshold at 0.05.",
    "All statistical analyses were performed using Jamovi (Jamovi, Sydney, NSW Australia, Version 2.3) and GraphPad Prism (GraphPad Software, Boston, Massachusetts USA,Version 10).",
    "A total of 4,302 email addresses for inclusion in the survey were collected from the list of journals in the appendix."
  ]
}